and looked for Third Uncle myself.

873
00:43:15,120 --> 00:43:16,159
This means

874
00:43:16,520 --> 00:43:18,159
you knew your Third Uncle isn't the one.

875
00:43:18,159 --> 00:43:18,719
Yes.

876
00:43:19,080 --> 00:43:19,919
I knew long ago

877
00:43:19,919 --> 00:43:22,199
