882
00:43:33,280 --> 00:43:35,280
Hence, there's no way Third Uncle
would've given

883
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:36,959
fake notes to Third Aunt for repayment.

884
00:43:36,959 --> 00:43:37,840
Because in doing so,

885
00:43:37,840 --> 00:43:38,800
